# Timesheet Database System - PostgreSQL Schema Documentation

## Overview
This document provides complete documentation for a PostgreSQL-based timesheet management system. The database consists of six interconnected tables that track staff, clients, projects, departments, and time entries.

---

## Database Architecture

### Entity Relationship Summary
```
staff_details (1) ──→ (1) staff_accounts
staff_accounts (1) ──→ (N) clients (as account manager)
staff_accounts (1) ──→ (1) departments (as department head)
staff_accounts (N) ──→ (1) departments (as department member)
clients (1) ──→ (N) projects
departments (1) ──→ (N) timesheets
staff_details (1) ──→ (N) timesheets
clients (1) ──→ (N) timesheets
projects (1) ──→ (N) timesheets
```

